        # install
        
        **Only available in test.pypi now**
        
        ```shell
        python3 -m pip install Flask==1.1.2 requests==2.25.0 pycryptodomex==3.9.9
        python3 -m pip install --index-url https://test.pypi.org/simple/ --no-deps khl.py
        ```
        
